ntrol group (P < 0.05). CONCLUSION Empathetic nursing with cognitive mindfulness therapy is beneficial in improving cancer-related fatigue, negative emotions, expectation level, and self-management ability in patients with longterm leukemia chemotherapy © The Author(s) 2022. Published by Baishideng Publishing Group Inc. All rights reserved
